{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>StarNomads</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your ship. Gather resources. Build weapons. Upgrade. Colonize planets. Protect your mothership. Destroy your enemies. In this Real-Time Strategy, Turn-Based, Roguelike game, you command a spaceship seeking to colonize various planets with hostile environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each turn, gather resources, build weapons and equipment, and make various upgrades that can take you further and further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171060/extras/8.jpg?t=1730380105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play solo, in co-op with up to four players, or in arena mode with up to eight players in frantic battles for planet colonization and resource domination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Diverse Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planets feature varied environments with unique obstacles. A new challenge every round. Build your strategy based on the obstacles ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlimited Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ship and weapon upgrades are limitless. Create strategies based on long-range damage, close-range combat, movement speed, or a mix of everything.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730380105","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171060/page.bg.jpg?t=1730380105","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171060/fb7e28ae27de625a306f8c92aba0bdce55928f4b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730